.TH i.emissivity 1 "" "GRASS 7.8.5" "GRASS GIS User's Manual"
.SH NAME
\fI\fBi.emissivity\fR\fR  \- Computes emissivity from NDVI, generic method for sparse land.
.SH KEYWORDS
imagery, emissivity, land flux, energy balance
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBi.emissivity\fR
.br
